abstract: >
  Open infrastructure and reference implementation for Argentine
  sociedades de IA (AI-operated companies) under the Anteproyecto de
  Ley General de Sociedades (art. 14, Sociedad Automatizada), announced
  by the Ministry of Desregulación on 28 April 2026 and sent to the
  Senate on 1 June 2026 (not yet law).
  The package comprises 33 Vercel AI SDK 6 compatible npm libraries
  (221 typed tools) spanning Mercado Pago, AFIP/ARCA identity +
  electronic invoicing, WhatsApp Business, banking, shipping, GDE/TAD,
  BCRA, IGJ, Boletín Oficial, fiscal calculators, and Mercado Libre
  integration; cookbook recipes; six RFCs (RFC-001..006, the first
  five with Zenodo DOIs) covering identity, agent discovery,
  cross-jurisdictional audit-log reciprocity, the operational-log wire
  format, the Ed25519 asymmetric upgrade path, and hash-chained ledger
  anchoring;
  conformance test vectors; a public certifier that scores any URL
  0-100 against RFC-002 + RFC-004 in seconds; a reference
  implementation that self-certifies at 100/100.
